A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Georgia's lineworkers and recognizing April 14, 2025, as Georgia Lineworker
2 Appreciation Day at the state capitol; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the profession of a lineworker is steeped in personal, family, and professional
4 tradition; and
5 WHEREAS, lineworkers are often first responders during storms and other catastrophic
6 events, working to make the scene safe for other public safety heroes; and
7 WHEREAS, lineworkers work with thousands of volts of electricity high atop power lines,
8 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, to keep electricity flowing; and
9 WHEREAS, lineworkers must often work under dangerous conditions, far from their
10 families, to construct and maintain the energy infrastructure of this state; and
11 WHEREAS, lineworkers put their lives on the line every day with little recognition from the
12 community regarding the danger of their work; and
