13 WHEREAS, it is most fitting and proper that the lineworkers of Georgia be recognized for
14 their effective and dedicated service to the people of the State of Georgia.
15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
16 the members of this body commend Georgia's lineworkers for their efforts in keeping the
17 power on and protecting public safety and recognize April 14, 2025, as Georgia Lineworker
18 Appreciation Day at the state capitol.
19 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
20 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
21 public and the press.
